Name: ITEM AVAILABILITY
Explanation: AVAILABILITY OF EACH SPECIFIC FEATURED PRODUCT OR SERVICE ASSOCIATED WITH THE FACILITY. THE AVAILABILITY IS WITH RESPECT TO PRODUCTION CAPABILITY.

Name: TARGET CONDITION AVAILABILITY
Explanation: INDICATES THE REASON WHY THE ENTITY IS NOT FULLY OPERATIONAL.

Name: UNIT CONDITION AVAILABILITY
Explanation: INDICATES THE REASON WHY THE UNIT IS NOT FULLY OPERATIONAL.
